overview: Master Google is an Internet marketing/SEO company that was founded eight years ago by SEO expert Ali Husayni. In addition to providing search engine optimization services to companies, Master Google also offers coaching and consulting to those interested in do-it-yourself SEO. The agency also maintains a blog that has attracted more than 10,000 subscribers and is packed with useful information about changes to Google’s algorithm that can affect a website’s ranking in organic search results. The blog is a good resource for companies interested in putting forth their best SEO effort to make sure their website can be easily found by potential clients and customers searching for particular products and services online.
